===============================================================================
                    DFBC - Delimited-File Bulk Changer
===============================================================================
                                README
===============================================================================

  This is a simple app developed in Ruby to make bulk changes in a 
delimited-file, like CSV.
  Basically you can make changes in a column for only one row or for entire 
file.

  It was done on my spare time, just to beginning to learn Ruby.
  (I know, there are a lot of mistakes!)

